languages.text: "Наконец свежий воздух. Воистину мы не ценим то, что имеем".
"Some fresh air at last. Truly we are at fault for taking such things for granted."

languages.text: “终于呼吸到新鲜空气了。我们一直认为这些东西理所当然，这实在是大错特错。”
languages.original_text: "Some fresh air at last. Truly we are at fault for taking such things for granted."

languages.text: "Endlich frische Luft. Wir dürfen solche Dinge nicht als selbstverständlich hinnehmen."

languages.text: « Enfin de l'air frais. On ne réalise pas à quel point c'est précieux jusqu'à ce que l'on en manque... »
languages.original_text: "Some fresh air at last. Truly we are at fault for taking such things for granted."

languages.text: «Aire fresco, por fin. Error nuestro por asumir que algo así siempre estará disponible».
languages.original_text: "Some fresh air at last. Truly we are at fault for taking such things for granted."

languages.text: 「ようやく新鮮な空気が吸えるますね。いつでも吸えるもんだと思っていた我らのミスです」
languages.original_text: "Some fresh air at last. Truly we are at fault for taking such things for granted."

traits.locale_text: 「ようやく新鮮な空気が吸えるますね。いつでも吸えるもんだと思っていた我らのミスです」

languages.text: "Nihayet temiz havaya kavuştuk. Böyle şeylerin değerini bilmediğimiz için hata bizde aslında."
languages.original_text: "Some fresh air at last. Truly we are at fault for taking such things for granted."
